      "title": "Welcome to Raines Perspectives",
      "URL": "https://rainesinternational.wordpress.com/2016/10/06/welcome-to-raines-perspectives/",
      "short_URL": "http://wp.me/p7C5yw-2kA",
      "content": "<hr />\n<p>Just a quick note to welcome new readers to Raines Perspectives, a new feature on Raines International&#8217;s website. For fifteen years, Raines International, a premier retained executive search firm based in New York City since 1969, has posted analysis, studies and profiles on its consultant-focused website <a href=\"http://www.ConsultantTrack.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://www.ConsultantTrack.com</a>.</p>\n<p>Today, Oct. 6, Raines International launched Raines Perspectives, which will feature great content across functions including consulting, management and human resources. On Raines Perspectives (<a href=\"http://www.perspectives.rainesinternational.com\">perspectives.rainesinternational.com</a>), we&#8217;ll post more frequently and more content. We will continue sharing analysis on current business, diversity and leadership issues, data-based studies and interviews with executives and leaders. We will also host all of ConsultantTrack&#8217;s content and the ConsultantTrack website will re-direct to the Raines Perspectives homepage.</p>\n<p>With the launch of Raines Perspectives, we have a ton of new content we will be publishing throughout the next two weeks, including thoughts on diversity and turnaround strategies. We also invite you to <a href=\"http://perspectives.rainesinternational.com/signup\">register for the site</a> and <a href=\"http://rainesinternational.us13.list-manage.com/subscribe?u=7fc0f199360cbeabda7efb97a&amp;id=4f39671b06\">subscribe to our monthly newsletters</a> where we will share current opportunities and placements.</p>\n<p>We&#8217;d love to hear your feedback and any suggestions.  E-mail us at jdeoliveira@rainesinternational.com, ssmith@rainesinternational.com or reach out on <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/rainesint\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/rainesinternational\">Facebook</a>, or <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/rainesinternational\">LinkedIn</a>.</p>\n<p>If you aren&#8217;t already familiar with Raines International, our Park Avenue-based firm conducts global searches for C-suite executives and their direct reports. Read more <a href=\"http://rainesinternational.com/about-us.html\"> about us here.</a> Biographies for our leadership are available <a href=\"http://rainesinternational.com/leadership.html\">here</a>.</p>\n<p>With expertise in all major industry sectors and functional areas, our client base includes privately-held companies, publicly-held corporations, leading private equity and venture capital firms, and not-for-profits. We have been longstanding members of <a href=\"http://www.aesc.org\">the Association of Executive Search Consultants </a>and the International Association for Corporate Professional Recruitment.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
      "excerpt": "<p>Today, Oct. 2, Raines International launched Raines Perspectives, which will feature great content across functions including consulting, management and human resources. On Raines Perspectives, we&#8217;ll post more frequently and more content.</p>\n",
