      "title": "Chief Marketing Officer, High-Growth Inc. 500 Consumer Goods Company",
      "URL": "https://rainesinternational.wordpress.com/2015/02/05/chief-marketing-officer-high-growth-inc-500-consumer-goods-company/",
      "short_URL": "http://wp.me/p7C5yw-293",
      "content": "<p>Obtained a <strong>Bachelor of Engineering</strong> followed by an <strong>MBA</strong> in Marketing and Strategy from the <strong>Indian Institute of Management, Bangalore</strong>.</p>\n<p>Following business school joined the marketing team of a <strong>Multi-Billion Dollar Consumer Products Company</strong> as <strong>Brand Manager</strong>, where he gained international P&amp;L Brand Leadership experience during his six year tenure. Later joined a <strong>top-tier management consulting firm</strong> where he developed and implemented branding and P&amp;L strategies for CPG, Retail, and Beauty corporations.</p>\n<p>Later joined a <strong>Multi-Billion Dollar Food &amp; Beverage Company</strong> where he served as <strong>Senior Marketing Director</strong>. In this role, he managed P&amp;L, franchise equity, and brand strategies for various <strong>multi-billion dollar businesses</strong> across international markets, establishing a proven track-record of successfully leading large multi-functional teams.</p>\n<p>Recruited by <strong>Raines International</strong> to serve as the <strong>Chief Marketing Officer</strong> of a high-growth<strong> Inc. 500 Consumer Goods Company</strong>. In this role, he will drive the Company’s marketing function, setting its strategic marketing direction and leading market execution to grow revenue and increase the overall business value.</p>\n<p><strong>Next move?</strong> CEO</p>\n",
