      "title": "Director, Product Management, Multibillion-dollar Private Technology / Telecommunications Company",
      "URL": "https://rainesinternational.wordpress.com/2012/09/25/director-product-management-multibillion-dollar-private-technology-telecommunications-company/",
      "short_URL": "http://wp.me/p7C5yw-2bm",
      "content": "<p>Received his <strong>Master of Engineering in Computer Science and Master of Science in Aerospace Engineering</strong>.</p>\n<p>Spent 7 years at a <strong>Multi-billion dollar Enterprise Software Company</strong> as a member of the technical staff leading development of a database solution including functional design, product development, and testing.</p>\n<p>Earned his <strong>MBA</strong> from <strong>The MIT Sloan School of Management</strong>.</p>\n<p>Moved to a <strong>top-tier strategy consulting firm</strong> where his engagements included advising a mobile handset insurance company on market entry operations and a US based mining equipment company on its China growth strategy.</p>\n<p><strong>Recruited by Raines International</strong> as the <strong>Director of Product Management </strong>for a<strong> Multibillion-dollar Telecommunications Company</strong> developing the product strategy, features, and enhancements for the line while managing cross-functional teams to support pricing and channel strategies.</p>\n<p><strong>Next Move?</strong> Senior Director / Vice President Product Management / Senior Marketing Role</p>\n",
      "excerpt": "<p>Received his Master of Engineering in Computer Science and Master of Science in Aerospace Engineering. Spent 7 years at a Multi-billion dollar Enterprise Software Company as a member of the technical staff leading development of a database solution including functional design, product development, and testing. Earned his MBA from The MIT Sloan School of Management. [&hellip;]</p>\n",
